        <li>Facilitating smooth payment processes for all transactions.</li>
        <li>Assisting management in preparing internal reports on a weekly, biweekly, and monthly basis.</li>
        <li>Reconciling thousands of sales transactions from eight stores and the B2B division.</li>
        <li>Conducting internal audits in stores to ensure compliance with company policies and procedures.</li>
        <li>Preparing and maintaining Standard Operating Procedures (SOP) for procure-to-pay and order-to-cash activities.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Since joining Lucky Bundle, I have received some awards:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Q3 2023 Top Performer.</li>
        <li>Q2 2023 Top performer in Task Prioritization category.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This experience provided me with invaluable insights and skills, further enriching my expertise in accounting and finance.</p>
      
      <br/>

      <h1 class="text-xl font-light">
        <a
          href="https://logiframe.com"
          target="_blank"
          class="h-6 float-left hover:text-primary-400 transition-transform ease-in-out duration-100 z-10"
          class="text-red-500"><b>Logiframe</b>
        </a>
      </h1>
